				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Meraskus' turn begins while in rage</p><hr /><p>Meraskus can enter in a blind fury, acting recklessy. Meraskus is considered @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Off-Guard} until the start of its next turn, but has a +2 status to all his Strikes.</p><p></p>",
